  m_Name: Ace Die
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Title: Ace Dice
  Description: "Ace Dice are dice with speacial abilities that can only be used once
    per installment, but choosing not to use them during an installment will allow
    you to use them multiple times in another installment. \n\nAce Dice are triggered
    by clicking on them in your egg carton during a round.\n\nYou can only use 1
    Ace Die per run, and you pick which Ace Die you'll use before starting your run."
